{"cell_id": "r2c4", "row": 2, "col": 4, "text": "The specified Nx_Port is either not Connected, or\nis involved in an Established Connection based\non the setting of the Connection established bit.", "page": 52, "bbox": [318.69, 144.0, 537.31, 190.05]}
{"cell_id": "r3c1", "row": 3, "col": 1, "text": "", "page": 52, "bbox": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0]}
