{"cell_id": "r3c4", "row": 3, "col": 4, "text": "A connect-Request has been delivered to the\nspecified Nx_Port, but the Nx_Port has not yet\nresponded with a proper response frame and a\ndedicated connection does not yet exist.", "page": 52, "bbox": [318.69, 190.05, 537.31, 248.01]}
