{"cell_id": "r4c4", "row": 4, "col": 4, "text": "No connect-Request is stacked for the specified\nNx_Port on behalf of the requesting Nx_Port.", "page": 52, "bbox": [318.69, 248.01, 537.31, 282.03]}
