{"cell_id": "r7c4", "row": 7, "col": 4, "text": "The specified Nx_Port is involved in a dedicated\nconnection. The address identifier in bits 23-0\nidentifies the other Nx_Port involved in the\ndedicated connection.", "page": 52, "bbox": [318.69, 362.01, 537.31, 420.03]}
{"cell_id": "r8c1", "row": 8, "col": 1, "text": "Intermix mode", "page": 52, "bbox": [98.38, 420.03, 215.43, 523.35]}
