{"cell_id": "r9c3", "row": 9, "col": 3, "text": "1", "page": 52, "bbox": [279.37, 454.05, 318.69, 523.35]}
{"cell_id": "r9c4", "row": 9, "col": 4, "text": "The N_Port specified in the request is functioning\nin Intermix mode. An N_Port is functioning in\nIntermix mode if both the N_Port and the F_Port\nhave both previously indicated that each supports\nIntermix during Login.", "page": 52, "bbox": [318.69, 454.05, 537.31, 523.35]}
